    "body": "Hi @Maaark,\n\nThat is not currently doable sadly for now. We have proposals to allow deep control over the rendering of every widgets but it's not yet ready.\n\nFor now I would keep the whole line clickable. Even on a UX side it's always very tricky to force people to click a very specific area (cross) instead of a much larger one.\n",
